<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_601" id="299v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_601_r2l17">Mıcheln von Streıtperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_601_r2l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Mıchel als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> habt / daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l19">eẅch in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> vnd ſchulden haben ſullen vnd darauf geleyts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l20">eẅch vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu vns begert etc / das haben wır wol ver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l21"><expan>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> Alſo wenn Jr in den <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> xıııȷ <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l22">ſo ſüllt Jr vnd eẅr geprött knecht ʒu vnd von vns für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l23">vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . vnd bey vns für <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıııȷ tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l24">geleyt haben . Alſdenn wellen wır eẅr rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_601_r2l25">ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_601" id="299v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Micheln von Streitperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Michel, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> habt,
                                                daz wir ewch in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan>
                                                und schulden haben sullen, und darauf geleyts ewch
                                                und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> zu uns begert etc.,
                                                das haben wir wol ver
                                                <expan>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan>; also wenn ir in den
                                                  <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> xiiii
                                                  <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> zu uns
                                                  <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt, so süllt ir
                                                und ewr geprött knecht zu und von uns für uns und
                                                die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                                  <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und bey uns für
                                                  <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                                                iiii tag geleyt haben. Alsdenn wellen wir ewr rede
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
